                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310512-102-victim745 t18310512-102-viclabel601"></join>. I was in <placeName id="t18310512-102-crimeloc602">Milton-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18310512-102-crimeloc602" type="placeName" value="Milton-street"></interp>
