                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310512-102-off599 t18310512-102-crimeloc602"></join> on the 24th of April - a female passed, and said a boy was picking my pocket; I turned, and saw the prisoner with my handkerchief in his hand - he was six or eight yards off; I pursued, and when I got within five or six yards of him, he threw down my handkerchief - I pursued, and took him; a female took up the handkerchief, and delivered it to the officer - I had it safe ten minutes before.</p>
